de.bioforscher.singa.simulation.model.compartments

Class CellSection

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.bioforscher.singa.simulation.model.compartments.CellSection
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Nameable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    EnclosedCompartment, Membrane

    public abstract class CellSection
extends java.lang.Object
implements Nameable
    A CellSection is everything that can be considered a part of the cell. It is characterized by a SimpleStringIdentifier. The content of a cell section is defined by a set of nodes.
